WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:07.313
Hey, good morning family. I just wanted to say we did it. Praise the Lord, mission accomplished.

00:00:07.314 --> 00:00:33.427
When we set out to pray for the President back whenever the election was over, the Lord said, 'You must pray him through the inauguration, for there will be many attacks trying to come against him, against his life, and against the inauguration itself.'He said this is going to be a time of great intercessory prayer, and that's exactly what we set out to do.

00:00:33.428 --> 00:00:39.110
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, you're going to raise up a million-man and woman prayer army.

00:00:39.111 --> 00:00:53.597
You're going to pray throughout the whole world and change things in politics and things that I'm going to show you as a watchman on the wall.'That's exactly what we've set out to do on this channel—to pray to change things.

00:00:53.598 --> 00:01:02.812
That's what we named our church: Prayer Changes Things. Prayer Church was taken and Prayer Foundation was there, so we used Prayer Foundation.

00:01:02.813 --> 00:01:08.094
People ask why we use 'Foundation'; it’s because that's what they had in the state of Oklahoma.

00:01:08.095 --> 00:01:15.202
We're excited to call it Prayer Changes Things because that's what we believe here.

00:01:15.203 --> 00:01:24.925
Thank you for joining me in praying. I believe our prayers changed a lot of things these last 100 days.

00:01:24.926 --> 00:01:34.614
I don't know how many days that is from November 5th to January 20th, but it's a lot of days. God used us, ladies and gentlemen.

00:01:34.615 --> 00:01:49.999
Whenever He gave me this very strong warning about the trucks, the vans, and all the major attacks I saw trying to come upon America, I believe we delayed it, because the trucks didn't disappear.

00:01:50.000 --> 00:02:04.985
What I saw in the spirit did not just disappear. All I know is that when we pray with our whole heart as believers, we have authority over the devil.

00:02:04.986 --> 00:02:15.479
I know beyond a shadow of a doubt that we have that authority because I've seen it work. I've seen prayer change things over and over again.

00:02:15.480 --> 00:02:33.659
People get upset and say, 'You should have a little fruit of something.'Just because you have a window of time where you protected the President to get him in and it didn't manifest everything I saw, doesn't mean it went away.

00:02:33.660 --> 00:02:39.587
He said this is something that's going to take continual prayer throughout his presidency.

00:02:39.588 --> 00:02:49.016
There are a lot of bad people in our country right now that were let in across those borders.

00:02:49.017 --> 00:03:08.096
Just because you delayed or stopped something for a window does not mean it went away; it just means they have to re-evaluate because we exposed their agenda in the spirit realm and uncovered a plot.

00:03:08.097 --> 00:03:16.759
They may try to reassess and come at a different angle another day. You have to be smarter than that.

00:03:16.760 --> 00:03:22.326
When you uncover the enemy's plans, the enemy has to re-strategize.

00:03:22.327 --> 00:03:37.881
So, we pray and ask the Lord what their next plan is. The enemy is relentless. Our job on this channel is to continue to pray.

00:03:37.882 --> 00:03:49.314
It's amazing that so much of the world listened to that video instantaneously.

00:03:49.315 --> 00:04:02.034
People who are not familiar with the spirit realm and how things work when you pray are going to criticize and say that guy's flaky because they don't understand what God's called a watchman to do.

00:04:02.035 --> 00:04:12.353
A lot of believers say, 'You should have this or have that,'and I say that's why God didn't call you to tell people—because you're too worried about their opinions.

00:04:12.355 --> 00:04:20.454
I'm addressing this because it needs to be said; I'm not going to sweep it under the rug.

00:04:20.454 --> 00:04:28.619
Similar to other prophetic words that have happened in the past, I've told you all I do not believe I'm a prophetic voice.

00:04:28.620 --> 00:04:41.897
Some say I walk in the prophetic, but I believe I'm called to do what the people who mentored me trained me to do.

00:04:41.898 --> 00:04:58.936
Pastors and evangelists have poured into me, and I've listened to prayer teachings from my youth, sitting under intercessory prayer people like Sister Billye Brim and the WWPs.

00:04:58.937 --> 00:05:10.990
We expect to change things. The Lord warns, 'Warning, warning, warning; pray, pray, pray,'and we delay or stop them.

00:05:10.991 --> 00:05:19.262
That's what we are called to do on this channel. I want to keep driving this in with you all.

00:05:19.263 --> 00:05:30.439
That's what this channel's for, and that's what we will continue to do over the next four years plus.

00:05:30.440 --> 00:05:44.808
It's not just about America; it's going to be about praying over Ukraine and Israel. I've seen more stuff, but I've been slow to release it.

00:05:44.809 --> 00:06:00.439
I used to make a video the same day I got something from the Lord, but because the platform has grown so big, I'm taking the time to pray over what He's showing me.

00:06:00.440 --> 00:06:09.620
That is wisdom when you have millions of people following you.

00:06:09.621 --> 00:06:13.310
I had the word about the inauguration because I was praying.

00:06:13.311 --> 00:06:21.336
I asked, 'What are you going to do to stop these trucks and stop them from hurting all these people?'Where did the trucks go?

00:06:21.337 --> 00:06:32.063
He said, 'I'm going to bring in a major cold front.'I have this all on video; I can document it and show you.

00:06:32.064 --> 00:06:39.802
The Lord said, 'Brandon, I'm going to bring in a major cold front that is unusual.

00:06:39.803 --> 00:06:53.017
It will be so strong that they'll have to take it indoors. I will protect the people through the weather.

00:06:53.018 --> 00:07:01.912
It will be so frigid and the winds will be strong—a blast of cold air.'He said it to me three times.

00:07:01.913 --> 00:07:18.713
He said it will change the course of what I saw coming. Just like He said, it happened. My wife recorded it.

00:07:18.714 --> 00:07:40.372
She asked, 'Honey, should you tell them?'I said I was going to pray over it first, but it didn't give me enough time to make a video.

00:07:40.373 --> 00:08:01.708
People are cold and will not show up. In these cities, people are not moving around much because of an unusual cold snap.

00:08:01.709 --> 00:08:18.824
It will be a sustained cold snap, reinforced three times. You will see this as it alters the way people move.

00:08:18.825 --> 00:08:43.060
This is very unusual and deep. It will flow down into places like Florida, but I see deep purple up north in Ohio—deep purple cold.

00:08:43.061 --> 00:08:56.177
The Lord is doing it to protect the people. It's about the inauguration.

00:08:56.178 --> 00:09:19.884
This will start this week and alter the weather to cooperate with the plan. People won't come outside when it's really cold.

00:09:19.885 --> 00:09:34.634
Terrorists don't want to do stuff when it's really cold because they're looking for big crowds.

00:09:34.635 --> 00:09:59.838
Our prayers are altering the weather. He's working on our behalf.

00:09:59.839 --> 00:10:16.274
I keep seeing it being reinforced, pulling it down, and changing things so people don't want to travel. What's coming is to distract and deter.

00:10:16.275 --> 00:10:36.318
The Lord said, 'Call this and pray for Trump.'I heard today to pray that the judge's plan to try to convict him on the 10th be foiled in the name of Jesus.

00:10:36.319 --> 00:10:45.229
We say to that foul devil from hell rising up inside this man: you are bound in Jesus'name.

00:10:45.230 --> 00:11:00.498
You will not succeed in this plan. We have authority over this demonic spirit, and your plans are coming to naught.

00:11:00.499 --> 00:11:15.398
We call the Supreme Court justices to rise up and defeat this plan. These plots are over in the name of Jesus.

00:11:15.399 --> 00:11:22.527
The Supreme Court justices will rule in our favor, and it will happen quickly.

00:11:22.528 --> 00:11:27.693
The weather changed and got really cold; it was a Siberian front.

00:11:27.694 --> 00:11:35.430
From what I understood, it was the coldest it's been in over 40 years.

00:11:35.431 --> 00:11:40.679
We give God all the glory because He can use the weather to change things.

00:11:40.680 --> 00:12:06.944
If the world isn't hearing Him, He can use the elements of nature to protect.

00:12:06.945 --> 00:12:19.599
Look how big our God is, that He would use the weather to protect our President and the people.

00:12:19.600 --> 00:12:38.163
I saw those drones and the trucks, but He made it so cold it would be miserable to go out. Then He brought the people into the stadium.

00:12:38.164 --> 00:12:51.902
We interceded for the stadium; I saw that and brought a video out way before they even announced the parade and ceremony would be held there.

00:12:51.903 --> 00:12:56.535
We got that glimpse from some sisters in Australia to warn everybody.

00:12:56.536 --> 00:13:25.171
It's not all about me; other watchmen saw something in advance.

00:13:25.172 --> 00:13:40.628
So we started interceding for the stadium. We're never blindsided by the enemy's plans.

00:13:40.629 --> 00:13:55.686
Thank God for communion; we're going to take it today and rejoice. If you're a skeptic, stick around.

00:13:55.687 --> 00:14:05.104
We saw in New Orleans—God rest their souls—the attack the Lord showed us in prayer at my flower bed.

00:14:05.105 --> 00:14:15.877
